commit message: Remove extra newline between badges in README

Remove GameSettings, use SharedPreferences to store game settings instead

This ensures that the user's currently selected board size and number of
colors will be kept after an app restart.
Replace recursive flood fill algorithm with an iterative one

Add gameFinished flag to stop games from being won multiple times

Users used to be able to press another color button very quickly
before the EndgameActivity had launched, have the game register
another win, and launch another EndgameActivity. Adding the
gameFinished flag stops this.
